auth.consentAdditionalInfoTitle: Further information and right of revocation
auth.consentAdditionalInfoText: I agree to share my fitness data with my Personal Trainer for the purpose of providing me with bespoke support in achieving my health & fitness goals. My fitness data will be stored in my EGYM profile and will be visible and transferable on an ongoing basis to my Personal Trainer. Data such as my master data, my training progress, my activities as well as analyses and training plans are transferred. My consent is voluntary and can be revoked by me at any time with effect for the future (e.g. in the settings of the EGYM profile at <0>egym.com</0>). Further information, including the right of revocation can be found in our privacy policy.
auth.mirrorOptInToggleLabel: Share my data with the gym
auth.mirrorOptInToggleDescription: Yes I confirm, that my EGYM profile is linked to my gym profile and, for this purpose, the data stored in the profiles are transmitted to the other profile and are thus continuously synchronized and updated. <highlightText>Sharing your data with the gym allows trainers to provide better member care to you.</highlightText> For more information and the right of withdrawal see <moreInfoLink>here</moreInfoLink>.
auth.mirrorOptInAdditionalInfoTitle: More information and the right of withdrawal
auth.mirrorOptInAdditionalInfoText1: Yes, I give my consent that my EGYM profile will be linked to my gym profile* of the gym(s)/home club(s) I set in the app and, for this purpose, the data stored in the profiles are transmitted to the other profile and are thus continuously synchronised and updated. I can withdraw my consent at any time. For more information and the right of withdrawal see our privacy policy.
auth.mirrorOptInAdditionalInfoText2: Linking the profiles allows my gym(s)/home club(s) I set in the app to view my training progress, my activities and my own EGYM analyses from my EGYM profile and provide me with my training plans and analyses, making it even easier for me to adjust the EGYM equipment to my needs, and further support me in my effort to achieve my goals. My consent is voluntary and may be revoked at any time with effect for the future (for example, in the EGYM profile settings).
auth.mirrorOptInAdditionalInfoText3:
*To link the profiles, the same email address must be used for your gym and EGYM.
Therefore, if necessary, please update your master data at your gym.
